window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Three vengeful spirits. One broken woman. One night.</b></p> <p>Harlow can't live with herself after the traumatic events of a fateful Halloween night two years ago. Half-broken then, she's shattered now. The only way forward is to go back to the abandoned house where it all happened and pay the ultimate price for her sins.</p> <p>But the house isn't empty. Three vengeful spirits lie in wait, vowing to destroy the woman who sent them to hell. Given just one night of freedom, they will bleed every second dry, taking all their rage, suffering, and hatred out on her.</p> <p>The three inflict agony, twisted with pleasure until all secrets spill out of their coffins in the hallowed hours of the darkest night. Blood splatters the walls of the haunted house until cries of depraved pleasure wipe away sins and horrors past.</p> <p>But what will happen when dawn rises, locking the gates of hell once and for all?</p> <p>The rules are clear. Pain for pain. Blood for blood. Death for death.</p> <p>Ghosts of Halloween <i>is a dark, spicy, why-choose romance with sword crossing for mature listeners. A complete list of content warnings can be found on the author's website.</i></p>"; 
